    <item>
      <title>What is FOMO in crypto - 避免 FOMO 的建议。 | What is FOMO in crypto - Advices to avoid FOMO.</title>
      <link>https://dev.to/market247_io/what-is-fomo-in-crypto-advices-to-avoid-fomo-hdk</link>
      <description>&lt;div id=&#34;page-content-inner&#34;&gt;&lt;p class=&#34;crayons-layout&#34;&gt;&lt;main id=&#34;main-content&#34; class=&#34;crayons-layout__content grid gap-4&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;article-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;article class=&#34;crayons-card crayons-article mb-4&#34; id=&#34;article-show-container&#34;&gt;&lt;header class=&#34;crayons-article__header&#34; id=&#34;main-title&#34;&gt;&lt;/header&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;crayons-article__main&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body&#34; id=&#34;article-body&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt; 使用 Market247，首先检查什么是加密货币中的 FOMO。 由于加密货币市场的波动性，可以体验 FOMO 的投资者更有可能在没有做足够研究的情况下购买硬币或代币。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--SEDZLT7Z--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/3qs68boknhkjrkvwq96q.jpg&#34; class=&#34;article-body-image-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--SEDZLT7Z--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/3qs68boknhkjrkvwq96q.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;图片说明&#34; width=&#34;700&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt; 有很多技巧可以避免 FOMO。 首先，进行自己的研究。 这是您可以采取的最重要的行动。 永远不要根据其他人在做什么或在说什么来做出选择。 进行自己的研究，只在您相信的情况下进行投资。 其次，你制定一个计划并遵循它。 当你有一个计划时，你可以轻松地遵循它并抵御 FOMO 的诱惑。 清楚地了解您的目标和您愿意投资的金额。 这使您可以在不受感情影响的情况下做出决定。 最后，要有耐心。 由于加密货币市场可能非常不稳定，因此耐心很重要。 不要让 FOMO 影响你的很多财务选择； 而是等待合适的机会。 如果您不进行投资，请不要担心； 还有其他机会。 不要让 FOMO 导致你看不到你的目标。 最重要的建议是投资者因此必须充分理解“什么是加密货币中的 FOMO”，&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; 查看详情： &lt;a href=&#34;https://market247.io/what-is-fomo-in-crypto&#34;&gt;https&lt;/a&gt; ://market247.io/what-is-fomo-in-crypto &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/article&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/main&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;section class=&#34;crayons-card crayons-card--secondary text-padding mb-4 print-hidden&#34; id=&#34;bottom-content-read-next&#34;&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0&#34;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;mattferrin 个人资料图片&#34; class=&#34;crayons-avatar__image&#34; width=&#34;100&#34; src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--FdKOLprH--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/175230/ca08ac15-950e-42b5-a493-b751fdb4694d.jpeg&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0&#34;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;thiagocolen 个人资料图片&#34; class=&#34;crayons-avatar__image&#34; width=&#34;100&#34; src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Qk9vnrnu--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/244487/d5a97e83-5715-481b-9816-bacf6bb5fc2a.jpeg&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0&#34;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;布克代码个人资料图片&#34; class=&#34;crayons-avatar__image&#34; width=&#34;100&#34; src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--NVHiU8_L--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/40578/7d5a837a-3143-420f-b9a6-c0f5431d6532.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0&#34;&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;c_yatteau 个人资料图片&#34; class=&#34;crayons-avatar__image&#34; width=&#34;100&#34; src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--jNmIyn0Y--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/870600/0306cbd9-5d18-425c-b478-b7c33203b116.png&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;p class=&#34;opacity-75 pt-1&#34;&gt; 考特尼·亚托——&lt;time&gt; 一旦暂停，market247_io 将无法发表评论或发布帖子，直到他们的暂停被解除。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;unsuspend-modal-content&#34; class=&#34;hidden&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt; 解除暂停后，market247_io 将能够再次发表评论和发布帖子。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;unpublish-all-posts&#34; class=&#34;hidden&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt; 一旦取消发布，market247_io 的所有帖子都将隐藏起来，只有他们自己可以访问。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&#34;mt-2&#34;&gt; 如果 market247_io 没有被暂停，他们仍然可以从他们的仪表板重新发布他们的帖子。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&#34;mt-2&#34;&gt; &lt;label&gt;笔记：&lt;/label&gt; &lt;textarea id=&#34;note_content&#34; class=&#34;crayons-textfield note_content&#34;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;flag-user-modal-content&#34; class=&#34;hidden&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt; 感谢您保护 DEV 社区 👩‍💻👨‍💻 的安全。 您可以通过以下方式标记 market247_io：&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&#34;crayons-field&#34;&gt;&lt;input type=&#34;radio&#34; id=&#34;flag-user-radio-input&#34; class=&#34;crayons-radio&#34;&gt; &lt;label class=&#34;crayons-field__label&#34;&gt;降低 market247_io 的所有帖子的可见度&lt;/label&gt;&lt;p class=&#34;crayons-field__description&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;javascript:void(0);&#34; id=&#34;report-inappropriate-content&#34;&gt;报告其他不当行为&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;unflag-user-modal-content&#34; class=&#34;hidden&#34;&gt;&lt;p&gt;取消标记 market247_io 将恢复其帖子的默认可见性。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;原文: &lt;div id=&#34;page-content-inner&#34;&gt; &lt;p class=&#34;crayons-layout&#34;&gt; &lt;main id=&#34;main-content&#34; class=&#34;crayons-layout__content grid gap-4&#34;&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;article-wrapper&#34;&gt; &lt;article class=&#34;crayons-card crayons-article mb-4&#34; id=&#34;article-show-container&#34;&gt; &lt;header class=&#34;crayons-article__header&#34; id=&#34;main-title&#34;&gt; &lt;/header&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;crayons-article__main&#34;&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;crayons-article__body text-styles spec__body&#34; id=&#34;article-body&#34;&gt; &lt;p&gt;With Market247 check What is FOMO in crypto first. FOMO stands for &#34;Fear of Missing Out&#34; that is the feeling of worry or anxiety brought on by the fear of missing out on something important or valuable. Because of the volatility of the cryptocurrency market, investors who can experience FOMO are more likely to buy coins or tokens without doing enough research.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--SEDZLT7Z--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/3qs68boknhkjrkvwq96q.jpg&#34; class=&#34;article-body-image-wrapper&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--SEDZLT7Z--/c_limit%2Cf_auto%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_auto%2Cw_880/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/articles/3qs68boknhkjrkvwq96q.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Image description&#34; width=&#34;700&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;There are many tips to avoid FOMO. Firstly, Make your own research. This is the most important action you can make. Never base your choices on what other people are doing or saying. Make your own research and only invest in case you believe.&#xA;Secondly, you make a plan and follow it. When you have a plan, you can easily follow it and fend off the lure of FOMO. Be aware of clearly your goals and the amount of money you are willing to invest. This allows you to make decisions without being affected by feelings.&#xA;Lastly, Be patient. Because cryptocurrency markets can be quite volatile, patience is important. Don&#39;t let FOMO affect a lot of your financial choices; instead wait for the right opportunity. Don&#39;t worry if you don&#39;t make an investment; there are other opportunities. Don&#39;t let FOMO cause you to lose sight of your objective. The most important advice is that investors must therefore fully comprehend &#34;What is FOMO in crypto,&#34;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xA;Cre: &lt;a href=&#34;https://market247.io/&#34;&gt;https://market247.io/&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;See detail: &lt;a href=&#34;https://market247.io/what-is-fomo-in-crypto&#34;&gt;https://market247.io/what-is-fomo-in-crypto&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/article&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/main&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;section class=&#34;crayons-card crayons-card--secondary text-padding mb-4 print-hidden&#34; id=&#34;bottom-content-read-next&#34;&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/mattferrin/blocked-for-2-months-2-weeks-and-counting-ad4&#34; class=&#34;crayons-link mt-6 block&#34;&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0&#34;&gt; &lt;img alt=&#34;mattferrin profile image&#34; class=&#34;crayons-avatar__image&#34; width=&#34;100&#34; src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--FdKOLprH--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/175230/ca08ac15-950e-42b5-a493-b751fdb4694d.jpeg&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/thiagocolen/data-structures-linked-lists-ffb&#34; class=&#34;crayons-link mt-6 block&#34;&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;crayons-avatar crayons-avatar--xl m:crayons-avatar--2xl mr-4 shrink-0&#34;&gt; &lt;img alt=&#34;thiagocolen profile image&#34; class=&#34;crayons-avatar__image&#34; width=&#34;100&#34; src=&#34;https://res.cloudinary.com/practicaldev/image/fetch/s--Qk9vnrnu--/c_imagga_scale,f_auto,fl_progressive,h_100,q_auto,w_100/https://dev-to-uploads.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/user/profile_image/244487/d5a97e83-5715-481b-9816-bacf6bb5fc2a.jpeg&#34;&gt; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;/div&gt; &lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;http://pages.feedbinusercontent.com/scrimba/how-html-css-and-javascript-work-10k&#34; class=&#34;crayons-link mt-6 block&#34;&gt; &lt;div class=&#34;flex items-center&#34;&gt; &lt;span class=&#34;cr